    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA356-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu varaivu maṟukkappaṭṭu āṟṟāṉākiya talaimakaṉ taṉṉeñciṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what HE said to his own heart, being unable to bear it when the marriage was refused.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA356">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            nilantāḻ maruṅkiṟ ṟeṇkaṭaṉ mēynta</l>
<l>            vilaṅkumeṉ ṟūvic ceṅkā laṉṉam</l>
<l>            poṉpaṭu neṭuṅkōṭ ṭimayat tucci</l>
<l>            vāṉara makaḷirkku mēva lākum</l>
<l>            vaḷarāp pārppiṟ kalkirai yoyyu</l>
<l>            macaivi ṉōṉpaṟai pōlac celvara</l>
<l>            varuntiṉai vāḻiyeṉ ṉuḷḷa morunāṭ</l>
<l>            kātali yuḻaiya ḷākak</l>
<l>            kuṇakkutōṉṟu veḷḷiyi ṉemakkumār varumē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          You suffered, live, my mind,</l>
<l rend="indent">          in going [and] coming,</l>
<l rend="indent4">           as the unwearying enduring wing</l>
<l rend="indent2">          of the red-legged goose with shining soft feathers</l>
<l rend="indent2">          that grazed the clear sea on a side hanging down to the ground,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">nilam tāḻ maruṅkiṉ</term>: what is this supposed to mean, with reference to the sea?</note></l>
<l rend="indent2">          which carries permanently(?)<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">alku irai</term>: here we might have to take the mere verbal root as an adverb.</note> prey to [its] ungrown young one,</l>
<l rend="indent3">          that is dear to celestials damsels in heaven(?)<note place="foot">Here <term xml:lang="ta">vāṉ</term> apparently refers to a celestial world, which is situated high in the himalayas.</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent">          on the summit of the Himālaya with long peaks</l>
<l rend="indent">          where gold is found.</l>
<l>        A day will certainly come for us, as Venus appearing to the east,</l>
<l rend="indent">          when [our] beloved will be close [to us].</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
